dataIdInfo.idPurp: These data are being transferred from ConocoPhillips Alaska, Inc. (CPAI) to the Bureau of Land Management (BLM) and DOWL to support the Willow Master Development Plan Supplement to the Environmental Impact Statement (Willow SEIS).
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This dataset includes gravel footprints forAlternative E (previously Alternative BT2N) ofthe ConocoPhillips Willow Project.

This feature class was transferred from CPAI on July 11, 2022. The REV date field in the data attributes reflects the currentness of each individual feature within the feature class.

Consts.useLimit: For use by permission from ConocoPhillips.
